					<br />
					<hr size="2" width="100%" />
					Title: <b>Re: How do I move where blockchain is stored?</b><br />
					Post by: <b>CIYAM</b> on <b>October 15, 2012, 05:07:24 AM</b>
					<hr />
					<div style="margin: 0 5ex;"><div class="quoteheader"><a href="https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=118509.msg1272983#msg1272983">Quote from: 420 on October 15, 2012, 05:02:36 AM</a></div><div class="quote">not easy it seems<br /></div><br />Is it really that hard for you to create a desktop shortcut and change the target to the following?<br /><br /><div class="codeheader">Code:</div><div class="code">Target: &quot;C:\Program Files\Bitcoin\bitcoin-qt.exe&quot;&nbsp; -datadir=D:\btcdata<br /></div></div>
